When you have #depression, hope can be scarce.

In place of hope/forced positivity, consider curiosity:

What will the future bring?
How may I feel tomorrow, next week, or next month?
What will be different soon? 

You won't always feel this way!

#MentalHealthMatters #YouMatter

- elle se soigne bien (avec psychothérapies et/ou antidépresseurs, mais pas que!)
3/13
